      <title>塔利班称袭击巴基斯坦后不会使局势“升级”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/taliban-says-won-t-escalate-situation-after-hitting-pakistan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿富汗塔利班领导的政府上周末对巴基斯坦军事哨所发动了袭击，并表示不会使局势升级，但警告说，如果再次遭到袭击，将进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/taliban-says-won-t-escalate-situation-after-hitting-pakistan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 10:18:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄之锋总理警告全球风险，新加坡经济增长超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/singapore-growth-beats-estimates-as-pm-wong-flags-global-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡总理黄循财表示，2024 年新加坡经济表现好于预期，为新加坡明年应对更为复杂的国际环境奠定了坚实基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/singapore-growth-beats-estimates-as-pm-wong-flags-global-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 10:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国提高公务员工资以刺激支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/china-raises-salaries-for-government-workers-to-boost-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国决策者试图提振士气、刺激支出，给全国公务员带来了多年来的首次大幅加薪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/china-raises-salaries-for-government-workers-to-boost-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 06:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平称中国2024年GDP增​​长目标将达到5%左右</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/xi-says-china-s-2024-gdp-growth-expected-to-be-around-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平表示，预计2024年全年中国国内生产总值将增长5%左右，这表明世界第二大经济体有望实现官方目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/xi-says-china-s-2024-gdp-growth-expected-to-be-around-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 06:06:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华盛顿特区市长穆丽尔·鲍泽称她与特朗普进行了“很好的会谈”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/dc-mayor-muriel-bowser-says-she-had-great-meeting-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普经常把华盛顿特区描绘成一个城市地狱，但华盛顿特区市长穆里尔·鲍泽表示，她周一与当选总统进行了一次“很棒的会谈”，并“对我们将继续找到共同点感到乐观”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/dc-mayor-muriel-bowser-says-she-had-great-meeting-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 04:41:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港政府上诉法院就高尔夫球场住房问题作出的裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/hong-kong-government-appeals-court-ruling-on-golf-course-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港政府正在对一项法院判决提出上诉，该判决暂停了在专属高尔夫球场部分区域建造公共住房的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/hong-kong-government-appeals-court-ruling-on-golf-course-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 02:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国对弹劾总统尹永哲发出逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/s-korea-court-issues-arrest-warrant-for-impeached-leader-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[调查人员称，韩国法院对陷入困境的总统尹锡烈发出了逮捕令，他因短暂的戒严令而被停职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/s-korea-court-issues-arrest-warrant-for-impeached-leader-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 00:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飞机失事促使韩国领导人暂停政治斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/plane-crash-prompts-south-korea-leaders-to-pause-political-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在短短几周内两位领导人被弹劾后，一场致命的飞机失事导致韩国敌对政治阵营暂时停止了旷日持久的权力斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/plane-crash-prompts-south-korea-leaders-to-pause-political-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国回应美国动物园虐待大熊猫谣言 展现善意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/china-fights-rumors-of-panda-abuse-at-us-zoo-in-sign-of-goodwill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在候任总统唐纳德·特朗普即将重返白宫的几周前，中国试图稳定与美国的关系，中国严厉打击了有关华盛顿一家动物园虐待大熊猫的谣言。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/china-fights-rumors-of-panda-abuse-at-us-zoo-in-sign-of-goodwill</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 07:34:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统弹劾程序如何进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/south-korea-president-impeached-who-s-in-charge-now-what-happens-next-for-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国国会投票弹劾总统尹锡烈，理由是他实施了短暂的戒严令。此次投票开启了一个可能需要数月才能完成的程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/south-korea-president-impeached-who-s-in-charge-now-what-happens-next-for-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 08:54:55 GMT</pubDate>
